    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE RANDOM DUNGEONS</h2>Enter a dungeon, find a portal, escape with your life. No two runs will be the same, will you survive? <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000830/extras/3fcbe9a499294c3a3546041ec993c9d3.poster.avif?t=1730140902\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000830/extras/3fcbe9a499294c3a3546041ec993c9d3.webm?t=1730140902\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000830/extras/3fcbe9a499294c3a3546041ec993c9d3.mp4?t=1730140902\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HIRE INTERESTING HEROES</h2>Hire heroes and level up heroes of different classes to customize your playstyle. Be careful though, if a hero succumbs to the dungeon, he will be gone forever!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000830/extras/46a3f202a6afe874e9d24e153911880a.poster.avif?t=1730140902\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000830/extras/46a3f202a6afe874e9d24e153911880a.webm?t=1730140902\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000830/extras/46a3f202a6afe874e9d24e153911880a.mp4?t=1730140902\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FIND POWERFUL WEAPONS</h2>Dive into each dungeon with a goal of getting stronger! Those lucky enough to survive will be rewarded with a large arsenal of weapons, some may even be cursed...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000830/extras/95587ed91a1df0452afb0edbb528c4d7.poster.avif?t=1730140902\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000830/extras/95587ed91a1df0452afb0edbb528c4d7.webm?t=1730140902\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000830/extras/95587ed91a1df0452afb0edbb528c4d7.mp4?t=1730140902\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Procedurally Generated Dungeons<br></li><li> 5 Classes of Heroes<br></li><li> Hundreds of Weapon + Curse Combinations<br></li><li> Tons of Playstyle Customization</li></ul>",
